The paper discusses the application of machine learning techniques to discover efficient mathematical identities. This falls under the domain of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of attribute grammar and tree search algorithms also suggests a connection to data structures (cs.DS) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper involves mathematical optimization, which could be classified under scientific computing (cs.SC).
